<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="義解" xml:id="gsz0751a12shiFuZhang"><lb
ed="T" n="0751a12"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0751a12"/><head><date from-iso="+0960-02-09" key="j20717322132856" to-iso="+1127-06-18"><anchor xml:id="beg0751sgsz1"/>宋<anchor xml:id="end0751sgsz1"/></date><placeName key="PL000000023341">東京天清寺</placeName><persName key="A010011">傅章</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0751a13"/><persName key="A010011">釋傅章</persName>，俗姓彭氏，<placeName key="PL000000023486">開封東明</placeName>人也。厥父<persName key="A018968">諲</persName>，即<lb
ed="T" n="0751a14"/>邑甸之上農也，塵務之外，正見不回，恒讀佛<lb
ed="T" n="0751a15"/>經，懸解<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1343"/>詮旨。母<persName key="A018969"><anchor xml:id="beg0751001"/>邢<anchor xml:id="end0751001"/><roleName>氏</roleName></persName>甞夢入法宇，手探道<lb
ed="T" n="0751a16"/>器，因而娠焉。與<ref type="person" target="#A018968">父</ref>知懷非常之子，指腹誓<lb
ed="T" n="0751a17"/>令出俗。<date key="j20570832057448" from-iso="+0920-01-01" to-iso="+0920-12-31">年甫十一</date>，乃禮<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023486">本邑</ref>唯識師<persName key="A010012">祕<roleName>公</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0751a18"/>為師，一見異之。初授《淨名》、《仁王》、《法華》三經，<lb
ed="T" n="0751a19"/>及削髮去周羅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1280"/>，隨<persName key="A010012">祕<roleName>公</roleName></persName>遊<placeName key="PL000000005439">五臺</placeName>，<anchor xml:id="beg0751sgsz2"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0751sgsz2"/><persName key="A002144">文殊</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0751a20"/>應跡之地。其年受具。為息慈<ptr type="glossary" target="#g964"/>日，便於<placeName key="PL000000023331">浚郊</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0751a21"/><persName key="A010014">清朗<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>座下聽習《法華經》。後於<placeName key="PL000000025555">睢陽</placeName><persName key="A010016">道雅<lb
ed="T" n="0751a22"/><roleName>法師</roleName></persName>重溫前業，尋學《唯識》於<ref type="person" target="#A010012">本師</ref><ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g190"/>，頗揭厲<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1031"/><lb
ed="T" n="0751a23"/>于義津法水。又親附副僧錄<persName key="A018972">通慧</persName>「因明」，且臻<lb
ed="T" n="0751a24"/>其極章。日誦三經兼二戒本，講貫<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1247"/>訓徒，向二<lb
ed="T" n="0751a25"/>十載，未甞少輟。<date notBefore-iso="+0951-02-18" key="j20684542069542" notAfter-iso="+0954-02-10">廣順中</date>，左街僧錄<persName key="A010018">廣智<roleName>大師</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0751a26"/>薦聞于<persName key="A006584">周高祖</persName>，賜紫方袍。<date from-iso="+0964-02-21" key="j20732052073559" to-iso="+0965-02-09">大宋乾德二年</date>，左<lb
ed="T" n="0751a27"/>街僧錄<persName key="A010019">道深</persName>薦于<persName key="A003883">太祖神德皇帝</persName>，賜師號<lb
ed="T" n="0751a28"/>曰<persName key="A010011">義明</persName>。俄示疾而終于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023341">本院</ref>，春秋五十五，<lb
ed="T" n="0751a29"/>法歲三十六。未絕之前，命筆作偈警世，而<pb ed="T" n="0751b" xml:id="T50.2061.0751b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0751b01"/>贈諸朋執矣。所度弟子一十五人，以<date key="j20735152073515" when-iso="+0964-12-27">其年<lb
ed="T" n="0751b02"/>十一月十六日</date><anchor xml:id="beg0751sgsz3"/>卜<anchor xml:id="end0751sgsz3"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000023467">京</ref>之南原，用<anchor xml:id="beg0751002"/>茶<anchor xml:id="end0751002"/>毘之法，<lb
ed="T" n="0751b03"/>薪盡火滅，得舌且不灰，眾歎戒德。門人檀<lb
ed="T" n="0751b04"/>信共立塔焉，則<date from-iso="+0972-01-24" key="j20760992076482" to-iso="+0973-02-10"><name>開寶</name>五年</date>也。先是<ref type="person" target="#A018968">厥父</ref>恒<lb
ed="T" n="0751b05"/>務《法華經》，終後焚之，亦舌不壞。子父同驗，<lb
ed="T" n="0751b06"/>實為罕有。<placeName key="PL000000023307">相國寺</placeName><persName key="A010028">清慧<roleName>大師</roleName>彝炳</persName>為《塔銘》<lb
ed="T" n="0751b07"/>焉。</p>
